playstore_details.title: Blockchain explorer for Ethereum : BANKEX Scan
playstore_details.description:
In the realm of the blockchain, detailed transaction accounting is enormously important. Not only does it allow for searching and receiving of complete information about specific transactions, but it can also provide market analysis of the digital economy. There are many platforms that record blockchain transactions, but they do have some disadvantages, including overly complex interfaces and repeated work disruptions.

To solve these problems, BANKEX decided to create BANKEX Scan —  an improved service for conducting Ethereum transactions with a user-friendly interface and more stable operation.

BANKEX Scan is a platform developed for cryptocurrency fanatics as well as those who are new to the world of ethereum blockchain. The platform’s customer service will devote greater attention to users’ requests and complaints. The BANKEX team expects BANKEX Scan to become a path that leads new users to BANKEX and then helps them find their way further into the world of blockchain and Ethereum chain.

With BANKEX Scan you can track transactions and every ERC-20 wallet balance, search by wallet, transaction id, or hash, and check all transactions for ERC-20 tokens. Get more 
ethereum info. We plan to add QR code for ETH Wallet scanning later. 

You can also explore blockchain ETH and any ERC-20 token blockchain without downloading the whole blockchain. Like in blockchain applications, you can get the Ethereum project information and read data from the network directly on your device.

The Ethereum blockchain has millions of users and transactions, and with BANKEX Scan you can track them all with just one app. Join the army of cryptocurrency Ethereum users! ERC20 tracker helps you to check every ERC-20 wallet and stay informed about what is happening. The Ethereum chain is on your device, including classic stats and graphs from the protocol, and the wallet explorer is the best way to check all the ETH wallets. 

Currently, this application supports only blockchain exploring, but later we will add notifications and a history of blocks and transactions. This is not a Bitcoin or Ethereum wallet, this is the search engine and blockchain explorer for all ERC-20 cryptocurrencies, like an etherscan.io, ethplorer.io, electroneum, ethersurface or etherchain. 

If you have an account at any Ether mining pools (like ethermine, ethfans, f2pool, miningpoolhub, nanopool, dwarfpool, bw.com, nicehash, ethpool, coinotron, ethermineru, waterhole, malaysiaethpool, coinmine, mymininghub, mining.sk, 2miners, zet_pool, gpuminepool, uleypool, gigantpool, anorak.tech, ethblockchain.us, comining.io, minergate, suprnova, maxhash, soyminero, etherdig, arsmine, chileminers, zion, xeminer, 1stpool, fullhashed, pool.sexy, virtualmining, aurora_pool, ethergrab.us, buriedone, noobpool, edgestile.io, antpool, coinfoundry, ethereumpool.club, ucrypto, miningcity.org, vaux-all, 99miners, poolmining.org, thesevendwarfs, canadianethereumpool, kratos, ethmine.club, ethmypool, ethertrench) you can use this app to track your mining rewards. Just enter your wallet address and you will know about every transaction!

You can use this ERC20 wallet crypto tracker to monitor multiple blockchains and know everything about yours or any other wallet. We have plans to add Favorite wallets soon, so you can add any wallet to Favorites and track all the transactions there, as in the etherscan.io, ethplorer.io, electroneum, ethersurface or etherchain. Also, Favorites will be added to Ethereum block explorer to save blocks with your transactions and show it to your friends, for example as proof of a successful ERC-20 tokens transfer. Even if you are using Ether classic tokens, you will get all the Ethereum info and stats. Soon you will be able to search and track wallets by public address and by QR-code, view wallets’ balance, transaction history, transactions info, blockchain txhash and total crypto amount.
